channel.description:
[b][b]Hello everyone on here. Im Wise Nubcake aka Explosive. Or here Aaronvdw Wise Nubcake is my name in the whole runescape private thing world. On servers i call myself Explosive cause of anoyying people asking me for things. So im Wise Nubcake , coder of Heaven Pkz. It is an Delta/Pk-Jad based server. I've put over 30% new things in it , made a new client together with one of my best friends in the rsps world Hyperion. He made over 60% new things to the client and i also added 15% new things into it. It took us alot of time and we enjoyed to make this source and client. But cause of our host problems we wanted to make the source usefull. As coder i decided that i wanted to release my source into the public. Lot of people asked if they could have it ( over 250 people ) and they will be happy if they see this. Well thanks for the attention. Here comes the source and the client from Heaven Pkz !
New Futures and new added things - What can you expect ?
Recoulered Dragon Armour - Full white dragon & full black dragon + cavaliers and fitting capes. Lot of new added customs like - Cigarette , Sunglasses , Godswords , Death Cape , customs whips and lot more ! 3 new minigames , 100% working + rewards and special shops The lava water from Pk-Jad , changed in source + client back to normal water ! Ownerzones , owneroffice and more staff places Kbd , Chaos elemental , KQ 2 forms , GWD , Giant Mole and lot more good monsters ! Dragon lair with 100% working random drops New home !!! Teleport + Death are there , shops , altars and gwd/ Kq entrances. all located on the island ! ::commands , easy to edit and all commands are in there ! ::updates , easy to edit and the latest updates can be find there !
And a lot more !!! Find it out yourself , look the pictures and download and the end of the page !!
A Video of all monsters , customs , places and lot more is coming soon ! Tomorrow night at the latest point.
.:.Some Pictures to see what the source has.:. The pictures are all made ingame and still on the base !
Starter Gear [img]http://i585.photobucket.com/albums/ss296/hyperion1994/StarterGear.jpg[/img]
New and Improved home !!! - New added [img]http://i582.photobucket.com/albums/ss264/Chicotje123/Thenewandimprovedhomeofheaven-pkz.jpg[/img]
Look at the minimap ! everything easy and nice. All shops are there. Sorry for the resized picture but i had to.
Low Train - New Added ! [img]http://i585.photobucket.com/albums/ss296/hyperion1994/lowtrain.jpg[/img]
Medium Train - New added ! [img]http://i585.photobucket.com/albums/ss296/hyperion1994/medtrain.jpg[/img]
High Train - New added ! [img]http://i585.photobucket.com/albums/ss296/hyperion1994/HighTrain.jpg[/img]
Newbiemini - New added low lvl minigame for lil bit starter cash [img]http://i585.photobucket.com/albums/ss296/hyperion1994/newbiemini.jpg[/img]
Avatarmini - New added A normal lvl minigame for random items and cash [img]http://i585.photobucket.com/albums/ss296/hyperion1994/avatarmmini.jpg[/img]
Working pk area's and working d claw spec ! - very nice ! [img]http://i585.photobucket.com/albums/ss296/hyperion1994/pking.jpg[/img]
Fun Pk - New added ! [img]http://i585.photobucket.com/albums/ss296/hyperion1994/funpk.jpg[/img]
You don't lose your stuff here !! It spawns you in the safe spot at the entrance of fun pk , when you die. It has an part with altars and pray altar for mage and pray.
It also has a skiller area , its just the basic one of Pk-Jad but its a great one. Fishing added 100% at catherby.
It was a plesure for me and my friend to make this and we hope much people can use it
Please leave a comment , a rate or anything else and post if you gonna try my source + client or maybe even gonna use it !
If something will appear or disappear and you need help , just PM me or add me on msn Aaron_wetering@hotmail.com i will try to fix it
I don't need the rep stuff
